\ls2\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Clear Goals: Define specific, measurable goals for the POC.\
\ls2\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Documentation: Thoroughly document the POC methodology, data used, and results.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Documentation of Findings: Document both positive and negative findings from the POC.\
